subject: Re:   File:London
body:
Hello Mr. Anthony Watson,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I appreciate the information you have provided regarding the negotiation with the Central Bank of Nigeria. It's interesting to hear about the part payment of my fund from their account with London Community Credit Union.

Could you please provide me with more details about this settlement? How did this negotiation come about, and what is the reason behind it? I would also like to know more about the Trade Exchange TED and its role in this process.

Looking forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Loree
